&lt;li&gt;Lead daily&amp;nbsp;check-ins&amp;nbsp;with the fabrication team to review priorities, deadlines, and task distribution&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and implement workflows that support clarity, efficiency, and creative&amp;nbsp;problem-solving&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track project progress and address challenges proactively&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement quality standards to ensure all deliverables meet studio expectations&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a project management calendar to keep all phases on track&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
