&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A thoughtful cover letter and resume.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;An updated portfolio: you are welcome to be creative, including photos of your own work and photos of classes you&#39;ve taught.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A proposal for the class you&#39;d like to teach.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
